  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Roguelite Dungeon Crawler!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/ba368abe52efae13c39457cdd3ebc943.avif?t=1772361022\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forgotten Cave is a roguelite dungeon crawler featuring endless procedurally generated dungeons. Collect loot, find powerful upgrades, and survive as long as you can in this mysterious cave!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/4a6378182e23c6a1f18babb268a53b0e.webp?t=1772361022\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.poster.avif?t=1772361022\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.webm?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.mp4?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Forgotten Cave</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forgotten Cave is a roguelite dungeon crawler that offers an exciting mix of action and exploration. Choose between three unique classes—Warrior, Archer, and Mage—each equipped with their own playstyle and abilities. Dive into procedurally generated dungeons, where every run is different, filled with dangerous traps, powerful enemies, and hidden secrets waiting to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/b6cf22db840c18717a5601bf56f48c21.webp?t=1772361022\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.poster.avif?t=1772361022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.webm?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.mp4?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a wide variety of loot and power-ups to enhance your character’s abilities, allowing for diverse builds and strategies. Face off against challenging bosses and uncover legendary treasures as you strive to survive the ever-changing depths of the Forgotten Cave.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forgotten Cave is a roguelite dungeon crawler featuring endless procedurally generated dungeons. Collect loot, find powerful upgrades, and survive as long as you can in this mysterious cave!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/4a6378182e23c6a1f18babb268a53b0e.webp?t=1772361022\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.poster.avif?t=1772361022\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.webm?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/83f0931c801742202aa416fd47b0b6c9.mp4?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Forgotten Cave</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forgotten Cave is a roguelite dungeon crawler that offers an exciting mix of action and exploration. Choose between three unique classes—Warrior, Archer, and Mage—each equipped with their own playstyle and abilities. Dive into procedurally generated dungeons, where every run is different, filled with dangerous traps, powerful enemies, and hidden secrets waiting to be uncovered.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/b6cf22db840c18717a5601bf56f48c21.webp?t=1772361022\" width=616 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.poster.avif?t=1772361022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.webm?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288560/extras/33b36b9fb25b4a0065722cf38678d83d.mp4?t=1772361022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features a wide variety of loot and power-ups to enhance your character’s abilities, allowing for diverse builds and strategies. Face off against challenging bosses and uncover legendary treasures as you strive to survive the ever-changing depths of the Forgotten Cave.</p>",
